{"title":"那盏灯光","authors":["远村"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":6,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"那盏灯光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那盏灯光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是那个湖南的农家子弟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"率先从很深的水底"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打捞上来的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那年头　贫血的中国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"根须总是伸向火热的煎熬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲把积压多年的泪水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾撒风中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那盏灯光　明亮而辉煌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它被无数年轻的手擎起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走在坎坷泥泞的道路上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感受春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那盏灯光生活在大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和天空之间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它总是让我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纯净若河流的波光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去润泽每一棵麦苗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在人世间饱满地歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那盏灯光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"至今仍灼灼"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}